caption:
We are so excited to announce & welcome our newest team member, Leah Smith! ❤️

Big News! I’m absolutely thrilled to share that after 5 years in real estate, I’ve joined Compass and the incredible Colleen Hadden Group! Growing up in Bucks County and moving to New Jersey over ten years ago, I am deeply committed to serving our South Jersey and Philadelphia neighborhoods. I’m a proud member of the Merchantville community, and my involvement in the school’s PTA and clubs are allowing me to create strong connections within our community and gain valuable insights into our area’s unique needs.
Joining The Colleen Hadden Group was an easy choice for me. This team embodies everything I believe in - genuine care for our clients and a steadfast commitment to delivering exceptional service. Their unwavering focus on putting our clients’ needs first truly resonates with me. And being part of a supportive group of women who prioritize both their clients and their families is incredibly inspiring. I’m beyond excited for this new chapter and the opportunity to continue serving you all with the utmost care and expertise. Whether you’re looking to buy, sell, or just want to chat about the real estate market, I’m here for you every step of the way.

Welcome to the team, @leahsmithrealtor
